*{{link-en|拉菲·卡西迪|Raffey Cassidy}} 配音 Becky

== 製作 ==
2019年2月，宣布根據{{link-en|麥可·莫普格|Michael Morpurgo}}同名小說改編成的[[動畫電影|動畫電影]]正在製作中，並由[[莎莉·霍金斯|莎莉·霍金斯]]、[[席尼·墨菲|席尼·墨菲]]、[[渡邊謙|渡邊謙]]和{{link-en|拉菲·卡西迪|Raffey Cassidy}}擔任配音。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2019/02/sally-hawkins-cillian-murphy-ken-watanabe-raffey-cassidy-animation-kensukes-kingdom-1202551372/|title='Kensuke's Kingdom': Sally Hawkins, Cillian Murphy, Ken Watanabe & Raffey Cassidy Join Michael Morpurgo Animation|first1=Andreas|last1=Wiseman|date=7 February 2019|work=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2021-03-26|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124230452/https://deadline.com/2019/02/sally-hawkins-cillian-murphy-ken-watanabe-raffey-cassidy-animation-kensukes-kingdom-1202551372/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年9月，在獲得新資金後電影進入製作中。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.screendaily.com/news/kensukes-kingdom-begins-production-with-new-finance-animation-partners-exclusive/5152909.article |title=‘Kensuke’s Kingdom’ begins production with new finance, animation partners (exclusive) |access-date=2021-03-26 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226214336/https://www.screendaily.com/news/kensukes-kingdom-begins-production-with-new-finance-animation-partners-exclusive/5152909.article |dead-url=no }}</ref>

